@page "/Account/ForgotPassword"

<PageTitle>Forgot your password?</PageTitle>

<h1>Forgot your password?</h1>
<h2>Password recovery is handled locally.</h2>
<hr />

<p>This launcher does not use email delivery or a mail server.</p>
<p>Ask the local owner to set a temporary password for your username, then sign in and change it from <strong>Account / Manage / ChangePassword</strong>.</p>
